                        <interp inst="t18690405-435-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted, at Chelmsford, on 18th February</hi>, 1868, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.—<hi rend="italic">
